column2: SELECT TOP # a.OBJID AS AKARI_ID, a.RA AS RA, a.DEC AS DEC, gsl.specObjID AS s1, gsl.SpecObjID AS s2, gsl.SPECOBJID AS s3, gsl.z AS redshift, n.distance AS angDist from MyDB.s8 AS a OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (a.RA, a.DEC, #) AS n LEFT JOIN galSpecInfo AS gsl ON gsl.SpecObjID = a.SPECOBJID
